      "description": "Mint condition. Garage kept. Original paint. No mechanical issues. Clean title.",
      "price": 45000.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 29
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Offering a truly exceptional, showroom-quality vehicle that has been fastidiously maintained in a climate-controlled garage. The exterior paint retains its original deep luster, protected by a professional-grade ceramic coating with zero stone chips, swirls, or imperfections. Inside, the cabin is indistinguishable from new; the premium leather upholstery remains supple with no bolster wear, and the 'new car' scent persists. This car has never seen rain or snow and has a documented history of being hand-washed only. Mechanically, it is flawless. Every service has been performed ahead of schedule at authorized dealerships, with a complete binder of receipts included. The engine bay is clean enough to eat off of, and the undercarriage shows no signs of road use. It sits on a fresh set of top-tier performance tires and includes both original keys, all factory manuals, and a custom car cover. This is a rare opportunity for a collector or enthusiast to own a pristine example of this model.",
      "price": 46500.0,
