    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Available for acquisition is an exceptional E46 M3, featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six power plant with individual throttle bodies and a factory-spec 8,000 RPM redline. This specimen has been meticulously maintained, featuring a documented VANOS overhaul and proactive rear subframe reinforcement to ensure structural integrity under high lateral loads. The Getrag 6-speed manual transmission offers crisp, short-throw engagement, paired with a variable M-Differential lock for superior power delivery. The chassis is dialed in with refreshed bushings and Bilstein dampers, maintaining the original suspension geometry and neutral handling balance. The exterior finish retains deep luster with no evidence of clear coat failure or oxidation, and the interior Nappa leather remains supple with no bolster wear. A mechanically transparent, turn-key example for the serious collector.",
